strings:
<voice_0x010013E3><se_def>*: Gojoshar! I see the horse you came with.
It is the most beautifullest white horse ever
I be seeing.
<voice_0x010013E4><se_def>*: So I thinking... Maybe you would trade it? For that I will give you my horses two.
<voice_0x010013E5><se_low>King Trode: YOU BLINKERED IDIOT! You'd swap my Princess for those bedraggled mares!?
<voice_0x010013E7><se_low>King Trode: ...I am not amused! Just who do you think Medea is, hm? I don't know...!

<voice_0x010013E8><se_def>*: Of course... Where your treasure is,
there your heart be also. Oh, well.
<voice_0x010013E9><se_def>*: If only I could give a horse that spiffing to my bride-to-be. That would certainly show her how much she means to me...
